{"content":[{"data":{"color":"black","source":"The Narrator","time_period":["0s AD"],"unique_sources":["John the Disciple"]},"nodes":[{"type":"prose","nodes":[{"marks":[{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"chapter"}],"object":"leaf","text":"1"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"1"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"This letter is from John, the elder.*\n\tI am writing to the chosen lady and to her children,* whom I love in the truth—as does everyone else who knows the truth— "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"2"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"2"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"2"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"because the truth lives in us and will be with us forever. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"3"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"3"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"3"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Grace, mercy, and peace, which come from God the Father and from Jesus Christ—the Son of the Father—will continue to be with us who live in truth and love. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"4"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"4"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"4"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"How happy I was to meet some of your children and find them living according to the truth, just as the Father commanded. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"5"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"5"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"5"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"I am writing to remind you, dear friends,* that we should love one another. This is not a new commandment, but one we have had from the beginning. "},{"marks":[{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"6"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"6"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"6"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Love means doing what God has commanded us, and he has commanded us to love one another, just as you heard from the beginning. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"7"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"7"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"7"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"I say this because many deceivers have gone out into the world. They deny that Jesus Christ came* in a real body. Such a person is a deceiver and an antichrist. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"8"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"8"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"8"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Watch out that you do not lose what we* have worked so hard to achieve. Be diligent so that you receive your full reward. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"9"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"9"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"9"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Anyone who wanders away from this teaching has no relationship with God. But anyone who remains in the teaching of Christ has a relationship with both the Father and the Son. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"10"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"10"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"10"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"If anyone comes to your meeting and does not teach the truth about Christ, don’t invite that person into your home or give any kind of encouragement. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"11"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"11"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"11"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Anyone who encourages such people becomes a partner in their evil work. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"12"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"},{"data":{"id":"COM-41"},"object":"mark","type":"keyPassage"}],"object":"leaf","text":"12"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"12"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"data":{"id":"COM-41"},"object":"mark","type":"keyPassage"}],"object":"leaf","text":"I have much more to say to you, but I don’t want to do it with paper and ink. For I hope to visit you soon and talk with you face to face. Then our joy will be complete."},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"12"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":" \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"13"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"13"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Jn","chapter":"1","verse":"13"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Greetings from the children of your sister,* chosen by God. "}]}]}],"colors":{"total":324,"black":324,"red":0,"green":0,"blue":0},"repeatedWords":["truth (6)","God (4)","us (5)","has (4)","love (4)","have (4)","Father (4)","Christ (4)","commanded (3)","children (3)","just (2)","chosen (2)","Jesus (2)","does (2)","Son (2)","am (2)","because (2)","another (2)","face (2)","beginning (2)"],"sources":{"The Narrator":{"words":324,"color":"black"}},"id":"S356"}